title: China-Norway free trade talks resume as PMs meet in Beijing
description:
Chinese Premier Li Keqiang welcomed Norwegian Prime Minister Erna Solberg in Beijing on Friday, as the two countries resume negotiations on a free trade agreement and continue to normalize relations after recent setbacks.
